description: Episode of Series "The New adventures of Winnie the Pooh". Three brand new adventures of Winnie the Pooh and the characters created by A. A. Milne. "Paw and order" Pooh and his partners take on the bad guys in a rootin'-tootin' cowboy play. "Fish out of water" There's something fishy going on in the Hundred Acre Wood when a trout migration threatens to overrun the village. "A Very large animal" Pooh Bear tries to make Piglet feel "big" but quickly discovers that it is no small feat!
